## ── ALPER-EU session data ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Session recordings contain participant data and can be several GB.
# Never commit these to a public repository.
recordings/

# Video files produced by the RealSense body tracker
*.avi

# Temporary gaze CSV created by standalone GazeAppAlpha mode
temp_gaze_data_*.csv

# Raw session CSVs (tobii_gaze.csv, upper_body.csv, hands_data.csv)
# and generated analysis files — all live inside recordings/ anyway,
# but this catches any that end up at the repo root by accident.
tobii_gaze.csv
upper_body.csv
hands_data.csv

# Log files
*.log

## ── Build directories ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
dist/